data.description: Welcome to this spacious 4-bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home with a refreshing pool. This beautiful property offers ample space for living and entertaining, with a fully equipped kitchen, comfortable living areas, and a private outdoor oasis. The primary suite provides a peaceful retreat, while the additional bedrooms offer versatility and comfort. The inviting pool area is perfect for enjoying sunny days and outdoor gatherings. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is a true gem for those seeking both relaxation and convenience.
